TVCLEAR   LLLLLLLLLLLLUUUUUUUUUUUU CCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCC
TVCLEAR:  Verb to clear image from TV channel
TVCHAN         1.0         16.     TV channel selection
                                     0 -> all on
----------------------------------------------------------------
TVCLEAR
Type: verb
Use:  Zero a number of gray-scale image channels in TV device
Adverbs:
  TVCHAN  Images to be cleared.  If outside range of 1 to NGRAY
          all channels that are now on are zeroed.
